kModal_main_2528230\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 20, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104hir1665702797793.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/hir1665702797793.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/hir1665702797793.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"hir1665702797793\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                          \n Define Keyboard Translation Table Library\n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Use this editor to define or modify keyboard translation tables.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hir1665702797793__p_d7154e1_d7155e1_d7156e1\">The keyboard translation tables supplied with Uniface are in the library USYS. At installation time, compiled versions of these tables are located in <span class=\"ph filepath\">USYS:usys.uar</span>.</p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"hir1665702797793__note_w121ab1b7b3_w122ab1b7_w123ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> You must import <span class=\"ph filepath\">libktt.usys.xml</span> from the\n        <span class=\"ph filepath\">/uniface/misc</span> directory of your installation before you can copy or\n      modify translation tables.</div>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hir1665702797793__section_kzf_2kg_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d419807e70\">Fields</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"hir1665702797793__ul_ww5_2kg_5cc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"hir1665702797793__li_d3542e1_d3543e1_d3544e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xrw1665702585620.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xrw1665702585620.html\" title=\"Use this property to briefly describe the development object in up to 256 Unicode characters.\">Description</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"hir1665702797793__li_d3545e1_d3546e1_d3547e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xgf1665702814722.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xgf1665702814722.html\" title=\"Contents of the translation table. It is better to provide as many definitions as possible, even if the device does not actually support a feature.\">Definition</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hir1665702797793__section_rfv_fkg_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d419807e97\">How to</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"hir1665702797793__ul_m4z_fkg_5cc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"hir1665702797793__li_d3548e1_d3549e1_d3550e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hir1665702797793__p_d7163e1_d7164e1_d7165e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xfr1665702814868.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xfr1665702814868.html\" title=\"Define your own device translation table if you want to modify how a device works, or address a device that is not yet supported.\">Define a New Translation Table</a>\n</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mew1705662925747.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Keyboard Translation Tables</a><p>A keyboard translation table maps a sequence of input codes received from a keyboard or database to logical function codes and characters recognized by Uniface.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dsd1665702981243.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Database Translation Tables</a><p>Database translation tables convert character strings during database input or output. This makes it possible to display characters stored in the database that are normally not visible (such as typesetting codes), or to store a key entered in a field as another string.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528230\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528230\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Define Keyboard Translation Table Library Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 20, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Define Keyboard Translation Table Library Use this editor to define or modify keyboard translation tables. The keyboard translation tables supplied with Uniface are in the library USYS. At installation time, compiled versions of these tables are located in USYS:usys.uar . Note: You must import libktt.usys.xml from the /uniface/misc directory of your installation before you can copy or modify translation tables. Fields Description Definition How to Define a New Translation Table Related Links Keyboard Translation Tables A keyboard translation table maps a sequence of input codes received from a keyboard or database to logical function codes and characters recognized by Uniface. Database Translation Tables Database translation tables convert character strings during database input or output. This makes it possible to display characters stored in the database that are normally not visible (such as typesetting codes), or to store a key entered in a field as another string. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}